 which stabilizes the\nquadrotor in case of an actuator fault. Overall, this paper presents a novel\nfault-tolerant controller design for quadrotor aircraft that effectively\naddresses actuator faults using a super-twisting sliding mode controller and\ncontrol allocation algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 17:22:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-28"}
