rging motor faults when the source training data contains very few distinct\ncategories. Incorporating FL may also provide a slight advantage by diffusing\nknowledge of health conditions between machines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 17:57:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-28"}
