e a dramatic improvement in generation diversity, which is\nvalidated by the objective Uniqueness and Novelty measures. More importantly,\nwe demonstrate the flexibility of IconShop with multiple novel icon synthesis\ntasks, including icon editing, icon interpolation, icon semantic combination,\nand icon design auto-suggestion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 17:58:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 May 2023 13:45:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 29 May 2023 14:26:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 7 Jun 2023 03:45:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-08"}
