dy ground effect, but also for two schooling\nhydrofoils in a side-by-side formation with an out-of-phase synchronization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Apr 2023 23:22:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-01"}
