ltigrid-based reference method. The hybrid algorithm opens an\navenue for the development of next-generation high-performance parallel\ncomputational fluid dynamics solvers for incompressible flows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Apr 2023 08:30:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 May 2023 08:56:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-05"}
