rvations in understanding high-mass star\nformation, both through single-dish maser monitoring campaigns and via their\ninternational cooperation as VLBI arrays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Apr 2023 10:32:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-18"}
